<font color="#FF0000">327 ABN. INF. ASS'N (VN) VETS</font><br>
<tt>Sat Feb  8 22:48:42 US/Eastern 1997
</tt><p>
Vietnam vets of the 1st and 2nd Battalions 327 Inf.(Abn), 1st Brigade 101st Airborne, who want to contact their Nam buddies should get in touch with me, Dave Cook. I served w/ &quot;C&quot; 1/327 '65-'66 and, for the last 9 yrs. have written a monthly column in &quot;The Static Line&quot; for the 327 Abn Inf Ass'n (Vn) and have compiled a roster of over 550 327 Nam vets w/fairly recent addresses and phone numbers. If you are interested in obtaining a 327 Roster, subscribing to &quot;The Static Line&quot; (A newspaper for the Airborne) or info about the 101st Airborne Division Association contact me by mail at Box 1300  Rt.2 Winthrop, Me.04364; phone:(207)377-2186 or via E-mail cookdsmg@mint.net
<p><code>-- cookdsmg@mint.net  (David S. Cook) </code><p>


